				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I agree with the previous post, these ghouls do not root.  I am a 35 Magician on the Nameless, and have some of these still con blue to me.  In this second hell I am able to solo very easy, and am gaining very decent experience from them.  There are 3 that always pop (rarely will a normal ghoul pop in their place) near the back door of the house, on the back wall where the waterfall is, near the Gazebo.  Every one so far drops bronze armor, small only.  While they are random drops, I have yet to get a helm or boots from them (hunted 3 days so far).  Perhaps this information will help.  Also seems to drop the ghould heart randomly, about every 10 kills or so for me.<BR>
<BR>
Relicbane Malificent &lt;Ancient Order of Power&gt;
